safetyTips: We are the only two chefs in the kitchen. We live on our own and only go from the house to kitchen and back again. We wear gloves and a mask and we deliver ourselves to minimise exposure.
name: London Kitchen Deliveries
description: We used to run a bespoke event catering business but are now offering fresh meals, virtual supper club experiences, fresh boxes, afternoon tea, wine and more, delivered contact-free. We deliver the items ourselves by car.
